{"word":"διαπεράω","slug":"διαπεράω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>διαπεράω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:διά\">διά</a>, περάω</el> ‘traverse’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πέραν\">πέραν</a></el>] ‘move across from one point to another’, <b><i>cross over,</i></b> of separated geographical areas, ordinarily by boat <b><a href='B:470 9:1'>Mt 9:1</a>; <a href='B:470 14:34'>14:34</a>; <a href='B:480 5:21'>Mk 5:21</a>; <a href='B:480 6:53'>6:53</a>; <a href='B:510 21:2'>Ac 21:2</a>.—</b>Of an uncrossable chasm<b> <a href='B:490 16:26'>Lk 16:26</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:διαπαρατριβή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:διαπλέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}